    "## Beta Estimation\n",
    "\n",
    "Following Frazzini and Pedersen [@frazzinipedersen2014], we estimate beta as the product of a correlation component and a volatility component:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\hat{\\beta}_i = \\hat{\\rho}_i \\cdot \\frac{\\hat{\\sigma}_i}{\\hat{\\sigma}_m}$$\n",
    "\n",
